Package: Nightjars
Title: Tracking and Visualizing Nightjar Populations by State
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jennifer", "Izquierdo", , "jenniferizquierdo@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to track and analyze the distribution and abundance 
    of nightjars across U.S. states, with a focus on the common 
    nighthawk. The package supports summarizing population trends, 
    visualizing geographic patterns, and aiding conservation research 
    for ornithologists, ecologists, and wildlife managers.
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
